1.0.0.name: wordpress/picasa-picture-embed
1.0.0.description: A plugin that allows you to embed picasa photos into your posts with the Wordpress 2.9 embedding feature. Include the url of the photo on a line of its own or between [embed] tags and the photo will be embedded.
